{"tid":502137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】不滿廉航託運要收費　莾男竟謊稱：「有炸彈」","createTime":"2017-12-17T14:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T16:18:48.000Z","uid":37661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76c0b5397126cfbeb71de8fcb8b13ae88a235333","tid":502137,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"不滿廉航託運要收費　莾男竟謊稱：「有炸彈」<br />\n<br />\n2017/12/16 17:49<br />\n<br />\n1名60歲陳姓男子，今天下午2時許，前往桃園機場第一航廈櫃臺報到時，因首次搭乘廉價航空，不滿行李託運還要另外收費，當地勤人員尋問行李箱內是否有刀、剪，陳男賭氣謊稱：「沒有刀剪，我有帶炸彈啦!」地勤人員不敢大意，立刻通知航警到場將人逮住。<br />\n<br />\n航警調查， 60歲台籍陳姓男子今天下午欲搭乘台灣虎航 IT-305 1440起飛班機前往澳門，因為該名男子經常出國旅行，但第一次搭乘廉價航空，不知道行李託運要收費一時氣不過，就說出有炸彈的話，航空公司人員立即通知航警到場處理 並將該男子帶回分隊調查，因楊男的行李並未送進機艙內，並未影響該架班機起降時間，訊後將依違反民用航空法移送偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n航警表示，根據《民用航空法》第105條規定，謊報炸彈屬於非法干擾行為，可處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或100萬元以下罰金。航空公司會將謊報者列入觀察名單，謊報者搭機時，會特別留意。（突發中心李俊淇／桃園機場報導） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171216/640_e04994b79c1cfc4fc055512c66d7bfe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171216%2F640_e04994b79c1cfc4fc055512c66d7bfe4.jpg&h=75ec9e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳男遭移送時表示感到相當後悔。李俊淇攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171216/640_d6fb268d9737127c2c806a40fc1d7e54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171216%2F640_d6fb268d9737127c2c806a40fc1d7e54.jpg&h=adb4b670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n航警不敢大意立刻將陳男帶回偵訊。李俊淇攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果日報 版權所有 不得轉載 NEXTmedia <br />\n&copy; 2017 <a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com&d=pPvdEGKV10J3HFLQn5UWZnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=db40a489\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com&h=6f49e187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tw.appledaily.com</a> Limited. All rights reserved.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171216/1260710/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171216%2F1260710%2F&d=pPvdEGKV10J3HFLQn5UWZnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=a4b395b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171216%2F1260710%2F&h=000bca1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171216/1260710/</a>"},{"pid":"684299cf479edd84a27adf66caeacadc52914f89","tid":502137,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67aac9402a6bcfd4ab4ae02f38ad288cc86cee39","tid":502137,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"揸正嚟做玩大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ed6ddb7faa0758b996608f0c38fed6d6bb9ff9","tid":502137,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bd74ac4a09681ad7e445d9ef6696ea0b2447e2","tid":502137,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c62cfd469f55704cbe9ad4d724d0883644d2bef","tid":502137,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"廢老無處不在"},{"pid":"4c00f0d576de9c090b82cae9128066afdaa00ed1","tid":502137,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"